net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.inline

Class RedefinitionDynamicTypeBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.DynamicType.Builder.AbstractBase<T>
      • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.inline.RedefinitionDynamicTypeBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The actual type of the rebased type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicType.Builder<T>

    public class RedefinitionDynamicTypeBuilder<T>
extends DynamicType.Builder.AbstractBase<T>
    A dynamic type builder that redefines a given type, i.e. it replaces any redefined method with another implementation.
